data.description: Lakefront beauty with rock waterfall views and multiple waterfront patios. You will not want to miss out on this elegant home in this highly desired gated Clovis Community of Stone Brook. This home is situated at the end of a cul-de-sac creating a serenity and views you will not find elsewhere. Greeted with a private courtyard overlooking the rock waterfall you enter to an open floorplan with a large living area, formal dining, dining and kitchen all sharing wall to wall windows with views of water features topped with premium automatic window treatments. The master suite also shares lake views with patio access and a master bath featuring a jetted bath tub and tile shower. While the home also has a second isolated bedroom with its own full bath access. Enjoy the community amenities just a short walk over the bridge such as the Pool, Spa, Club House, and Exercise Room. Schedule your private tour today!
